data.description: Welcome to your charming one-story retreat, just off Clear Creek Road and conveniently located down the street from Ft. Cavasos. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you approach, you're greeted by the inviting presence of front and backyard-covered porches – perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or relaxing in the evening breeze. Step inside to discover the timeless elegance of hardwood floors that adorn the main living area. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, providing both style and functionality for your culinary endeavors. Whether you're preparing a family feast or a quick meal, this kitchen is sure to inspire. The comfort continues in the carpeted bedrooms, offering cozy retreats for relaxation after a long day. The thoughtful layout ensures privacy and functionality for every member of the household. This charming abode offers not just a place to live, but a sanctuary to call home. With its convenient location and inviting atmosphere, this residence embodies the essence of comfortable living. Schedule a showing today!
